                            <div class="image-caption">
                                some caption
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="para-text">
                            Aarambh with the DDB Mudra, a media company, started working from a point of frugal innovation. The framework outlining the project were not so simple: (i) a desk that can be assembled by a 7 year old kid, (ii) can be repurposed for a school bag, (iii)
                            low priced and (iv) made from recycled materials. <br><br>“Looking back, I think the solution was right in front of our eyes,” says Sanuree Gomes, an art director from DDB Mudra, the firm responsible
                            for the design. “We wanted a material that was not only strong, but flexible and economical. We had just received a shipment at our office, and we had boxes lying all around us.”
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="margin:20px 0px;">
                    <div class="para">
