                            <div class="image-caption">
                                some caption
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="para-text">
                            Materials: Cardpaper sources from local businesses and recycling centers.<br><br>Shelf life: 6-12 months<br><br>Manufacturing cost: Rs. 15 / units<br><br>Production team: 10 women part of a self help group<br><br>Team: Shobha
                            Murthy, SHGs in Vidharba.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div style="margin:20px 0px;">
                    <div class="para">
                        <div class="para-title"> Total Impact
                        </div>

                        <div style="text-align:center;">
